Troubleshooting Tips
LinPEAS not executing:

Verify execute permissions: chmod +x linpeas.sh
Check if script was transferred correctly to container
Ensure sufficient disk space in container
Docker container issues:

Restart Docker service: sudo systemctl restart docker
Remove and rebuild containers: docker rm -f container_name
Check Docker logs: docker logs container_name
Python script errors:

Verify Python3 is installed: python3 --version
Install missing modules: pip3 install module_name
Check file paths and permissions
